name: astral friend
description:
If you could choose who you are, who would you be? 

Personifying positive thoughts, experiences, feeling and energy can help anchor you in waters you want to exist in. 

Your personal astral access allows you to create, modify and play with who you truly are without the constraints of the tangible world. 

We know who or what we are in dreams without knowing what we actually look like in this space.  

We can use this to build who we want to be.
